name: Altrucoin
public_notice: Altrucoin has migrated from old contract to a new one. Visit this post for more information. Old token page https://www.coingecko.com/en/coins/altrucoin-old.

description.en:
The Altruism Protocol is an ecosystem of decentralized applications building a DeFi lending platform for all tokens.

The protocol brings together an existing multi-dapp ecosystem, trustless defi lending, a modern utility token, charitable donations, and decentralized governance.
